"mins)\\ A moving short documentary about an English beef farmer who "
"transitioned his farm to sustainable, organic, plant-based agriculture."
msgstr ""
"[Vimeo](https://vimeo.com/293352305): 73 Cows (dir. Alex Lockwood, 15 "
"mins)\\Un conmovedor corto documental sobre un ganadero inglés que ha "
"cambiado su granja por una agricultura sostenible, ecológica y basada en "
"plantas."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-03-09-global-newsletter-49-1.md:314
msgid ""
