"[Best Vegan Lasagne](https://biancazapatka.com/en/vegan-lasagna-with-lentils-and-zucchini/) (I tweaked this a bit & prefer brown over red lentils, & pre-baked aubergine slices over zucchini - but however you do it this is delicious.)\\\n"
